%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-227wrLIpUoxknSPF289w0w">Trào ngoan thạch ảo tương - 嘲頑石幻相</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Tung/Tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-O0QMdXGuqU7N-RdUk0b62w">Trúc chi ca kỳ 5 - 竹枝歌其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Tung/author-8q1Pl4yTEAzPiO_vSuznIA">Tôn Tung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cao-V%C3%A2n/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-m%E1%BB%87nh-thi/poem-wYraddLLjpzMAKwu2fhNXQ">Tuyệt mệnh thi - 絕命詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Cao-V%C3%A2n/author-3c-CQSCCk16hIygvv2H0EA">Trần Cao Vân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Kh%C3%A1nh-D%C6%B0/V%E1%BA%A1n-Ki%E1%BA%BFp-t%C3%B4ng-b%C3%AD-truy%E1%BB%81n-th%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-LSgdJg2r4wQq7VoHw34x0g">Vạn Kiếp tông bí truyền thư tự - 萬劫宗秘傳書序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Kh%C3%A1nh-D%C6%B0/author-Bu-KUl9kbBmWLGXqoo-_Ag">Trần Khánh Dư</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
